  • Classes in com.fdmgroup.spring.timothy_chai_ecommerce_project.model used by com.fdmgroup.spring.timothy_chai_ecommerce_project.model
    Class
    Description
    Cart
    Represents a shopping cart for the customer The Cart class holds a set of CartItem objects which refer to Product classes.
    CartItem
    Represents a line item in the shopping cart The CartItem class encapsulates ordering information, holding reference to the Product class and other relevant information like the product quantity and subtotal.
    Customer
    Represents a Customer The Customer class is intended to represent customers in this application.
    Order
    Represents an order in the system.
    Product
    Represents products in the online shop The Product class encapsulates all product information like the name, available stock, price, and a URL to an image of the product Customers can view product information using respective getters, and add products to the cart through the use of the CartItem class
